From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniel Hiltgen <daniel@ollama.com>
Date: Mon, 9 Mar 2026 13:32:14 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] ggml: No-alloc mode

---
